high_descs: Go forward and face the counter on the right near the bottle.
Turn around and face the white stove with the microwave above.
Put the plate in the microwave, shut the door, open the door and take the plate out and shut the door.
Face the lower cabinets to the right.
Open the bottom, corner cupboard and put the plate in and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed plate in the cupboard.

high_descs: Go around the fridge ahead to the left and go straight, turn right at the blue plate on the counter.
Take the blue plate from the counter.
Turn around, go straight to the counter, turn left and go striaght to the oven.
Put the plate in the microwave above the oven. Turn on the microwave. Take the plate out of the microwave.
Put the plate in the bottom left cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot plate in a cabinet.

high_descs: Go left, then turn right, and go straight to the counter next to the fridge.
Pick up the plate on the counter, to the left of the bread loaf.
Turn around, then go straight, then turn left toward the stove.
Heat the plate in the microwave, about the stove.
Put the plate in the bottom left cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm plate in the cabinet.
